pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `dim_pekerja` ( `noPekerja` int(11) NOT NULL, `namaDepan` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `namaBelakang` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `extension` varchar(10) NOT NULL, `email` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `kodeKantor` varchar(10) NOT NULL, `laporan` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `jabatan` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `idPekerja` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`idPekerja`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `dim_pelanggan` ( `noPelanggan` int(11) NOT NULL, `namaPelanggan` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `namaDepan` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `namaBelakang` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `telepone` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `alamatJalan` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `kota` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `provinsi` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `kodePos` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `negara` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `noSales` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `kreditLimit` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT NULL, `idPelanggan` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`idPelanggan`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `dim_pesanan` ( `noPesanan` int(11) NOT NULL, `tanggalPesanan` date NOT NULL, `tanggalExperied` date NOT NULL, `tanggalPengiriman` date DEFAULT NULL, `status` varchar(15) NOT NULL, `komentar` text DEFAULT NULL, `noPelanggan` int(11) NOT NULL, `idPesan` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`idPesan`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `fakta` ( `id` int(10) NOT NULL, `amount` decimal(10,2) NOT NULL, `sk_pekerja` int(10) NOT NULL, `sk_pelanggan` int(10) NOT NULL, `sk_pesanan` int(10) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
